title.en: Shukujo no Kagami Yamemashita. Toki wo Gyakkou shita Koushaku Reijou wa, Wagamama na Imouto ni Furimawasarenai you Seikaku Waruku Ikinobimasu!
Hametsu End Kara Gyakkou Shitara, Nishuume wa Nazeka Aisare Route deshita - Yami Ochi Reijou wa Ouji e no Fukushuu wo Akiramenai (no ni Dekiaisareru)
Usso, Koushaku Reijou wo Oshinokete Ouji no Konyaku-sha (Kari) ni Natta Onna ni Tensei?
Himegimi wa Wakaki Shougun ni Oboreru
Doku-suki Reijou wa Kekkon ni Tadoritsukai
Hameraremashita ga, Shiawase ni narimashita - Kizumono Reijou to Hidamari no Madoushi
Kurokishi-sama kara Zenryoku de Dekiaisareteimasu ga, Sugomori Seijo wa Kyou mo Hikikomoritai!
Yarinaoshi Tensei Reijou Hazamaa Shitai no ni Dekiaisareru
Akugyaku Seijo desu ga, Aisuru Danna-sama no Oyaku ni Tachitai desu. (To wa Ie, Kirawarete Iru no desu ga)
Dare ni mo Aisarenai no de Yuka wo Migaite Itara Soko ga Seiiki-ka shita Reijou no Hanashi
Kokoro wo Tozashita Koushaku Kakka to Konyaku Shita Hazu na no ni, Naze ka Taisetsu ni Sasete Shimattemasu!
Itsuwari no Inaka Reijou, Osananajimi no Ouji-sama wo Kouryaku-chuu
Sono Akuyaku Reijou wa Kouryakuhon wo Tazusaete iru
